class Solution:
    def maxOperations(self, s: str) -> int:
        ret = 0
        n = len(s)
        suf = 0
        i = n - 1
        while i >= 0:
            # print("prei", i)
            if s[i] == '1':
                ret += suf
            else:
                # print("st", i)
                suf += 1
                while i >= 0 and s[i] == '0':
                    i -= 1
                i += 1
                # print("ed", i)
            i -= 1
                
            # print(i, ret, suf)
                
        # print(s[0])
        # print(s[1])
        
        return ret
